DESCRIPTION: a JS script to add ambient bar charts, "backbars", to popular sites
PROJECT PAGE: http://elzr.com/backbars
COMPATIBILITY: Currently works on Firefox thru Greasemonkey.
GOALS:
* To work in Google Chrome, Safari Greasekit, Opera.
* Work on more sites: Craigslist, Metafilter subsites..
* Better performance on busy sites.
* Use jQuery 1.4 (currently breaks for unknown reasons).


